        <item>
            <title>日本推出多功能藍牙 Cassette 機，可聽收音機、轉錄 Cassette 帶成 MP3</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/japanese-bluetooth-cassette/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japanese-bluetooth-cassette</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/japanese-bluetooth-cassette/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 11:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Cassette]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡式帶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[收音機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[藍牙喇叭]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1275331</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本 SANWA 近日推出一款具備多功能的藍牙收音機 400-MEDI050BK，結合傳統與現代技術，為用戶提供全方位音訊體驗。除了可以播放卡式帶，更支援 AM/FM 收音機功能，另外具備藍牙連接，甚至更可將卡帶播轉換為數碼格式，兼具懷舊與實用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_01-600x580.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_01-600x580.jpg 600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_01.jpg 931w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_02-501x580.jpg" alt="" width="501" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_02-501x580.jpg 501w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_02.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 501px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275362" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_09-694x325.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="325" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_09-694x325.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_09.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_10-493x580.jpg" alt="" width="493" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_10-493x580.jpg 493w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_10.jpg 765w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 493px" /></p><p>這款收音機可播放卡式帶功能，更能夠將音訊轉換為 MP3 格式，並儲存至 USB 手指或 SD 卡中。其藍牙功能允許與手機或其他裝置連接，用戶可輕鬆播放現代串流音樂。此外，裝置亦有 MP3 播放器，提供多樣化的音樂播放選項。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275357" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_04-392x580.jpg" alt="" width="392" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_04-392x580.jpg 392w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_04.jpg 608w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 392px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可以將卡式帶轉錄為 MP3 檔案</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275358" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05-581x580.jpg" alt="" width="581" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05-581x580.jpg 581w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05.jpg 901w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_05-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 581px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲最快僅需要 6 個步驟即可完成轉錄</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275360" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_07-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_07-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_07.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可轉錄至 SD 卡、USB 手指等</p><p>裝置設計上體積輕便，方便攜帶，在電源方面，這部卡式機可以使用電芯或交流電兩種供電方式，無論是室內居家享受還是戶外派對均可應對，用戶無需為電力供應或音源格式擔憂。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275361" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_08-551x580.jpg" alt="" width="551" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_08-551x580.jpg 551w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_08.jpg 855w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 551px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援電芯及交流電</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275359" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_06-694x505.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="505" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_06-694x505.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_06.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可充當藍牙喇叭</p><p>這款收音機售價為 13,800 日元（約港幣 690 元），顏色方面可選擇黑色或紅色，收音機以其懷舊外觀和現代功能成為家庭和旅遊愛好者的理想選擇。產品結合經典收音機的質感與現代技的便利，為音樂愛好者和卡式帶收藏家提供全新體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1275366" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_03-694x438.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="438" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_03-694x438.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/400medi050_03.jpg 1045w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://direct.sanwa.co.jp/ItemAttr/400-MEDI050">SANWA</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/15/japanese-bluetooth-cassette/wireless-home/audio-visual/">日本推出多功能藍牙 Cassette 機，可聽收音機、轉錄 Cassette 帶成 MP3</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
